Package com.googlecode.cqengine.query.parser.sql.grammar

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    SQLGrammarListener
    This interface defines a complete listener for a parse tree produced by SQLGrammarParser.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    SQLGrammarBaseListener
    This class provides an empty implementation of SQLGrammarListener, which can be extended to create a listener which only needs to handle a subset of the available methods.
